snippet.title: maybe: Interactive Stories | A Good Day To Be A Dog Ep 1
snippet.description:
You never had a proper kiss because of your big secret. But because of one little mistake, your secret comes back as a curse! Out of the three men, who will be the one with the key to undoing your curse?
.
.
Scenario by Nakwon / Artwork by Studio Shelter, Huku / Original Comics from WEBTOON™ (©Lee Hey)
.
Google Play ➤ https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.cinamongames.maybegv&hl=en_US
App Store ➤ https://apps.apple.com/us/app/maybe-interactive-stories/id1508286483
